2. Refer the proxy.pcap capture file given to you (faculty.amrita.ac.in/lekhas/labexam). Answer the following questions

a. How can you identify that captured frames use proxy server? Explain the interaction, need and significance of proxy server.
b. What is the IP address of the original host which has the original web page?
c. Does the proxy use authentication? Justify.
d. Justify why http uses a connection oriented reliable service with necessary screenshots.

